{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC13_ODI_620.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2d,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x199,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Ms. Odelia, I came to plaaay!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, I have been waiting.<CR>Now, let us get occupied."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Why are we getting occupied?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xad,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "To occupy ourselves from boredom.<CR>I have been waiting for your arrival."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xaf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Now, what shall we do today?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1a4,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, I brought you a souvenir!<CR>Ta-da, sweets!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Remember how you told me that you wanted to try eating something sweet?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x73,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "This is something sweet...<CR>It somehow...smells nostalgic."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I prepared these just for you.<CR>Please try eating one."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x74,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "If you insist, I have no reason to resist eating."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x75,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I was designed without the need to eat, but I am equipped with a meal processing function, as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Umm, don't think too hard and just give it a try."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see. Then I shall follow your advice. Even so, I wonder how long it has been since I have had a meal..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x185,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Let me see. I should search for the record of my last meal..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "L-Let's just stop thinking about all that complicated stuff."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x187,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "You are right. Now, if you will excuse me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x1b9,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "*munch* *munch* *munch*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Sweets can somehow make you happy,<CR>just by eating them!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "If you eat too much, you'll get fat,<CR>but it's hard to resist the temptation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x1ba,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "*munch* *munch* *munch*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I would like for you to know the charm that sweets have as well, Ms. Odelia."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "That's why I brought them here!<CR>So, how are they?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x1ba,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "*munch* *munch* *munch*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "If you liked what I brought today, there are more kinds that I can recommend."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "So I'd like to know what you think.<CR>Do you like them?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x1ba,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "*munch* *munch* *munch*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Umm, Ms. Odelia...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x1ba,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "*munch* *munch* *munch* *munch*"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "(Hahaha...there's no use, she's not listening to me.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x1bb,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "So these were sweets...<CR>Thank you very much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "H-How were they?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x14e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "As I said before, I have no need to consume meals."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x151,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "However, they were not bad. Sweets give off such an interesting sensation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x155,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Consuming meals will become a nice way of occupying my time to prevent boredom."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "(Hmm, I'm not too sure if she liked them or not...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x150,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "They were very gentle and melty and charming. It was an interesting phenomenon."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "(I'm glad she liked it.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "For your health, you should eat proper meals."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xad,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, as I said earlier, I was created by human hands."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xae,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "This body, that was created with advanced alchemy, does not require food nor sleep..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xae,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "And I will not become sick or die."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, th-that's amazing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0xaf,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "Yes, it is amazing. However..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x73,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "If it is something sweet, I would not mind eating it for you again. You should bring something again next time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "Okay, then please look forward to it!"
        }
    ]
}